item.title: Error: Port alredy in use?
item.dc:creator: @heathtech heathtech
item.description:
@heathtech wrote:

Did you make sure that the last server you were running was closed properly? I suggest you look for “cmd” in your processes of Task Manager to verify. If there is still an instance of one, you may need to end that task. If that doesn’t help, restart your computer. That will surely fix the problem.
